Implementation of Image Segmentation with Topic Random Field (Zhao,
Fei-Fei, and Xing).

References:
B. Zhao, L. Fei-Fei and E. P. Xing. Image Segmentation with Topic
Random Fields. European Conference of Computer Vision (ECCV), 2010

David M. Blei, Andrew Y. Ng and Michael I. Jordan. Latent Dirichlet
Allocation. Journal of Machine Learning Research, vol. 3,
pp.993--1022, 2003. 

